Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离爱丽丝的诞生只剩下一点点时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是「父亲大人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗真不是只会去见爱丽丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么不去实现  你们所深爱着的父亲大人的愿望呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行爱丽丝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  明日早晨  在n之领域恭候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人竟然和蔷薇水晶在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样都无所谓的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只能去战斗了的说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么要听从那种家伙的命令啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经完全想清楚了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了取回苍星石的蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能够逃避爱丽丝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会！一定还有其他方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你过去到处乱跑也只会妨碍我们的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我希望你可不要把我当作傻瓜吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种没半点威力的小提琴演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没用的说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧？拨弦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  你没听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过你不会战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  还有翠星石都说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…竟然是罗真…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过父亲大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算见过他也什么都改变不了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等于是什么都不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  什么都做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓把她的蔷薇圣母托付给了真红的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后都会和真红在一起的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石以后也要一直一直和翠星石在一起的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金  快看快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前拍的照片我做成海报了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～大家都太可爱了～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金和小雏的合照  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成超大版的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要钉在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  一定要买个画框才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用图钉钉在墙上实在是太可惜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后挂在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在正中间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  早饭好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就吃…花蛋汉堡扒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有练习比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭我会做更加更加好吃的的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…回来哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那么  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：{\fnふみゴシック\fe128}頼もう{\r}，是日本古代去道场踢馆时叫门用的话）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明叫你不要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不懂事的家伙的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀不来的话  爱丽丝游戏就没办法开始吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说我也是蔷薇少女中第一军师…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是碰到危险就夹起尾巴赶快逃跑的说哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗  罗真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说！父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对父亲大人的决定有异议…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要取回苍星石的蔷薇圣母的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒真红之前  再拿一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小金也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了吧？野蔷薇之前奏曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？完全没有用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二章  垂首士兵之进行曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快给我逃远点的说  金丝雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还能援助同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还满游刃有余的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你一个人又能做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你在瞄准哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要拿回苍星石的蔷薇圣母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最重要最重要的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用这把剪刀打败你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才尽兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗真！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红是为了阻止爱丽丝游戏才到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金的声音攻击竟然完全没有用…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就听真红的话不来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？少了一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被…被  被粉碎了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没有看别处的时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所面对的  可是我水银灯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是能找麻烦的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里发呆快给我过来的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你打算做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快从门那里逃跑的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道能挡住她多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你走一段的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小金还能战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在那里抱着头发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别罗嗦逞强了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再眼睁睁地  看着谁的蔷薇圣母被夺走了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  抓紧走的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要粉碎了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想其它的事情的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去门那里的说哦！金丝雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我现在就过去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我来救你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！为什么回来的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你也不用这么说吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就是一次拿两个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…翠星…石…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你没听见吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的爱丽丝游戏正在向正确的方向进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来…保护吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想从旁边抢走…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把翠星石的蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不给你…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静地燃烧着  愤怒的和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出真本事来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是对翠星石见死不救哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致失去之时刻的镇魂曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金能做到的  就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保护吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保护翠星石的蔷薇圣母！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于认真起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  借给  借给小金力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…不给你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石由我  由我来保护吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要再接近了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次  这次我要为大家派上用场吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对  绝对不会把翠星石交给你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一定要保护…她…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:21:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以…过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星…石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金  金丝雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个时候开始  我就一直在祈求着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈求那唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信那唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父亲大人的面前  爱丽丝正…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见
